Gov. Nasir El-Rufai of Kaduna State has felicitated with Christians as they celebrate the birth of Jesus Christ, urging them to pray for peace. The Christmas message from the governor was posted on his Facebook page. The message reads” This is to wish everyone in Kaduna State, Nigeria and the rest of the World a very Merry Christmas. ” May the peace and blessings encapsulated in the spirit of this season be with us throughout the rest of our lives. ” May the rest of our lives be the best of our lives. Amen.” Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.